                        Upravljanje svim igračima.
                    </p>
                    <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start pt-3">
                        <a asp-controller="Igraci" asp-action="Create" class="btn btn-success btn-sm px-4 py-2 fw-bold fs-6">Novi unos</a>
                        <a asp-controller="Igraci" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm px-4 py-2 fw-bold shadow-sm fs-6">Vidite Sve</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
